name: 金贝利·奎恩 Kimberly Quinn
intro: Kimberly Pita Quinn is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Gretchen on the FX television series Terriers[1] and for her role as Tess Masterson on the ABC Family series Twisted.[2] She also has made guest appearances on the television series Suddenly Susan, Nash Bridges, Diagnosis: Murder, NYPD Blue, Without a Trace, House M.D., Two and a Half Men and CSI: NY.
